title: Iranian Women’s Soccer Team a Manly Bunch . . .
text: Posts: 847 Iranian Womens Soccer Team a Manly Bunch . . . Iranian soccer fans were left reeling earlier this week after eight members of the womens national team were found to be men, the Al-Arabiya website reported on Monday. Mojtabi Sharifi, described as an official connected to the Iranian soccer league, said that the footballers have been playing with Irans female team without completing sex change operations. Iran....they would NEVER cheat at anything
